Description: Provides curated long-run series on Brazilian formal education,
    with a focus on school enrollment and educational attainment (years of
    schooling, literacy, level completion). Data are compiled and reconciled
    from heterogeneous official and academic sources (Censo Escolar, PNAD,
    Censo Demográfico, Anuário Estatístico do IBGE, Paglayan 2022, among
    others) into a single tidy schema, with explicit provenance, enabling
    descriptive analyses and the study of educational inequality across
    race, sex, income and location.
